    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find that looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or age. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine runs silently and powerfully, and every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the climate control, functions exactly as intended. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and comes with a full service history, offering the next owner a brand-new driving experience.",
