    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of the highest caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and maintaining its original factory luster. Meticulously curated and mechanically flawless, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection. Every surface and component reflects a standard of care that is simply unparalleled in the pre-owned market.",
